results.title: Drop-If-Exists
results.sql: DROP TABLE IF EXISTS hits ALL;

results.title: Reload-hits
results.sql: COPY INTO hits FROM 's3://repo.databend.rs/hits_p/' credentials=(aws_key_id='{{ "AWS_KEY_ID" | env }}' aws_secret_key='{{ "AWS_SECRET_KEY" | env }}') pattern ='.*[.]tsv' file_format=(type='TSV' field_delimiter='\\t' record_delimiter='\\n' skip_header=1);
